org.eel.kitchen.jsonschema.validator

Class InstanceValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eel.kitchen.jsonschema.validator.InstanceValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonValidator

    final class InstanceValidator
extends Object
implements JsonValidator
    The main validator

    Such a validator is only called when the schema syntax has been verified to be correct. It is also responsible to instantiate an ArrayValidator or ObjectValidator if necessary.

    See Also:
    JsonValidatorCache.getValidator(SchemaNode)
